ism|publisher=SAGE Publications|isbn=9781526415974|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Calossi|first=Enrico|year=2016|title=Anti-Austerity Left Parties in the European Union. Competition, Coordination, Integration|location=Pisa|publisher=Pisa University Press|isbn=9788867416653|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Cammack|first=Paul|year=2004|chapter=Giddens's Way with Words|editor1-last=Hale|editor1-first=Sarah|editor2-last=Leggett|editor2-first=Will|editor3-last=Martell|editor3-first=Luke|title=The Third Way and Beyond: Criticisms, Futures and Alternatives|publisher=Manchester University Press|isbn=97807190-65989|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Campbell|first=John|year=2009|title=The Iron Lady: Margaret Thatcher from Grocer's Daughter to Prime Minister|publisher=Penguin Books|isbn=9780099540038|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|editor-last=Campbell|editor-first=Heather M.|year=2009|chapter=Christian socialism|chapter-url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/socialism/Socialism-after-Marx#ref276341|title=The Britannica Guide to Political and Social Movements That Changed the Modern World|publisher=Rosen Education Service|ref={{harvid|Campbell 2009 (Christian socialism)}}}}\n: {{cite book|last1=Carmines|first1=Edward G.|last2=Layman|first2=Geoffrey C.|year=1997|chapter=Issue Evolution in Postwar American Politics|editor-last=Shafer|editor-first=Byron|title=Present Discontents|location=Chatham, New Jersey|publisher=Chatham House Publishers|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Carr|first=E. H.|year=1985|title=The Bolshevik Revolution 1917\u20131923|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Carson|first=Kevin|year=2008|title=Organization Theory: A Libertarian Perspective|location=Charleston, South Carolina|publisher=BookSurge|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|last=Carson|first=Kevin|year=2010|title=The Homebrew Industrial Revolution: A Low-Overhead Manifesto|location=Charleston, South Carolina|publisher=BookSurge|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite book|editor-last1=Chamberlain|editor-first1=Greg|ed